  {
    "task": "Provide a note on reserves for the last four years",
    "owner": "HEFCW",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Lynne Neagle AM: You did say that you would give the committee a note on reserves for the last four years,"
  },
  {
    "task": "Send a transcript to check for accuracy following the meeting",
    "owner": "HEFCW",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Lynne Neagle AM: And, as usual, you'll be sent a transcript to check for accuracy following the meeting."
  },
  {
    "task": "Increase QR funding in real terms",
    "owner": "HEFCW",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Sian Gwenllian AM: Have you carried out any kind of assessment of the impact of this level of research funding on universities and, indeed, on the Welsh economy?"
  },
  {
    "task": "Maintain QR funding at the same level for 2019-20",
    "owner": "HEFCW",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Sian Gwenllian AM: The allocation is exactly the same for 2019-20 as it has been for the past nine years."
  },
  {
    "task": "Provide £15 million in innovation funding to help universities access UKRI funding",
    "owner": "HEFCW",
    "deadline": "2020-21",
    "evidence": "Bethan Owen: One aspect that we do intend to fund—and this is from Diamond, as well as Reid—is to place funding back into the system for innovation."
  },
  {
    "task": "Improve the accessibility of information on university income and expenditure",
    "owner": "HEFCW",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Janet Finch-Saunders AM: The council's remit letter for the 2019-20 academic year from the Minister does ask you to consider how you'd increase openness and transparency around the use of fee income."
  },
  {
    "task": "Support and fund growth in part-time provision",
    "owner": "HEFCW",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Hefin David AM: Part-time student numbers are bucking the trend in Wales, as I understand it, and we are seeing a bigger increase in Wales of part-time numbers than elsewhere in the UK."
  },
  {
    "task": "Maintain the attractiveness of Welsh universities to students",
    "owner": "HEFCW",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Bethan Owen: And, just to add, I think the key bit of that is maintaining the attractiveness of Welsh universities to students, because a large proportion are coming not from just Wales, but from England and internationally—so, that's a key part—"
  },
  {
    "task": "Develop a vision for research and innovation",
    "owner": "HEFCW",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Dr David Blaney: And, then, there's also the recommendation from Reid that Wales needs to be better embedded in the conversations that are going on on a UK-wide basis, so the Welsh Government has established a presence in London in respect of research, and we have a colleague in HEFCW who is fractionally embedded in the United Kingdom Research and Innovation specifically to respond to that recommendation."
  }
]

